window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A new town, new dungeons, and a new adventure.</b></p> <p>Daniel Chai only ever wanted to be an Adventurer. Born with a Gift of Healing that steals his memories and past experiences as its fuel source, Daniel must weigh his heart's desire with his gift as he attempts to clear his first ever dungeon. Along the way, he'll meet true friends like the Catkin Asin and the Northerner Omrak as he learns what it truly takes to be a professional Adventurer in Brad.</p> <p><i>The Adventures on Brad</i> is a light fantasy novel set in a LitRPG world where everyone is born with a Status Screen and Classes.</p> <p>This bundle collects the second arc of Adventures of Daniel and friends in Karlak and the Beginner Dungeon. The bundle includes books four to six:</p> <p></p> <ul> <li><i>The Arena's Call</i></li> <li><i>The Adventurer's Bond</i></li> <li><i>The Forest's Silence</i></li> </ul>"; 
